OL,3,CStudent nurses could drop out of
OL,4,Ccourses amid financial pressures, RCN
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMore than 32,000 student nurses could
OL,8,Fdrop out of their courses in the next
OL,9,Ffew years because of financial
OL,10,Fpressures, struggling services and
OL,11,Fworsening pay prospects, a leading
OL,12,Fhealth union is warning.
OL,14,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN)
OL,15,Fsaid its study showed that without
OL,16,Faction to make the career more
OL,17,Fattractive, the Government's plans to
OL,18,Freform the NHS would be undermined.
