OL,3,CStudent nurses could drop out of
OL,4,Ccourses amid financial pressures, RCN
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FStudent nurses in England have been
OL,8,Fdropping out since the nursing bursary
OL,9,Fwas scrapped in 2016, but tens of
OL,10,Fthousands could leave before
OL,11,Fgraduating by 2029, said the RCN.
OL,13,FAn RCN survey of nursing students in
OL,14,FEngland from earlier this year showed
OL,15,Fthat seven in 10 are considering
OL,16,Fquitting due to financial pressures.
