OL,3,CStudent nurses could drop out of
OL,4,Ccourses amid financial pressures, RCN
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FAddressing the debt burden and easing
OL,8,Fcost-of-living pressures is the best
OL,9,Fway to reduce the dropout rate,
OL,10,Falongside increasing nursing pay to
OL,11,Fmake the career more attractive, the
OL,12,FRCN said, adding that in the health
OL,13,Fservice in England, there are 31,774
OL,14,Fnursing posts currently vacant.
