OL,3,CStudent nurses could drop out of
OL,4,Ccourses amid financial pressures, RCN
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FRCN General Secretary Professor Nicola
OL,8,FRanger, said: "The students of today
OL,9,Fare the nurses of the future, but for
OL,10,Ftens of thousands, the unbearable
OL,11,Fweight of graduate debt, lack of
OL,12,Fsupport with living costs and prospect
OL,13,Fof low pay is set to push them out of
OL,14,Fthe profession before they qualify.
OL,15,FThis is a tragedy for them and
OL,16,Fpatients.
