OL,4,Ccourses amid financial pressures, RCN
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Transforming care cannot happen
OL,8,Fwithout investment to transform
OL,9,Fnursing. That means changing the way
OL,10,Fwe recruit into the profession and
OL,11,Fmaking it a more attractive career by
OL,12,Fraising pay."
